node.text: With a little imagination and some Little People friends (and some glue and cotton balls), you’ll be playing in a winter wonderland. Check out the festive fun from @5.min.crafts . ❄

node.text: Celebrating 90 years of play. And shapes and ABCs and rainbow rings and Little People and puppies and telephones with eyes and happy apples and BigFoot and singing sloths and let’s be kids! #FP90

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Fisher-Price on September 17, 2021 tagging @buffalobills, @ochbuffalo, and @wegmans. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text:
Help our hometown team by heading to @wegmans  to purchase your Fisher-Price® Little People® Let’s Go Buffalo! figure set. 100% net proceeds from the sale of this set will go to The Children’s Hospital of Buffalo Foundation. (@ochbuffalo)*

*Beginning September 1, 2021 through December 31, 2022, an amount equal to half of the purchase price paid by the consumer for this set (excluding taxes or other charges) when purchased in-store at participating Wegmans Food Markets will be donated by Fisher-Price to The Children’s Hospital of Buffalo Foundation providing philanthropic support to John R. Oishei Children’s Hospital to ensure access to high quality health care for the moms, kids and babies of Western New York. Offer open only to residents of NY, PA, NJ, VA, MD, and NC.  No portion of the purchase is tax deductible. For more information about The Children’s Hospital of Buffalo Foundation, visit FOROCH.org. Offer may be extended in Mattel’s sole and absolute discretion. Mattel reserves the right to suspend or cancel the promotion in its sole discretion for any reason including in the event of force majeure.
